{
  "stem": "1828.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The-- obviously, the Nazis disappeared, our overseers, they-- they-- they ran away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we knew that the Allies, somebody is approaching in this direction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They contaminated the water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They poisoned the water--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--before they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On purpose, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- there was one SS woman hiding out in a bunk under somebody's bed, whom they got rid of.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know whether they did, or whether she had befriended some women and that they helped her and they just simply let her go.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the Allies, the British army, came, we heard them from a distance already.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They looked great to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They brought a tank of water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we couldn't drink the water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They arrived, and they were so shocked that some-- some of them could not-- could not function.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they spoke through the bullhorn, you're free now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Don't panic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Don't do this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, the usual instructions you would give people that are-- that we have-- we have food for you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But be slow about eating it, and all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Mother had told us already, don't eat much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Just taste something, put it away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they-- they were just great.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When they were replaced a few weeks later, it was no comparison.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They had-- they-- they were just unbelievably wonderful to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- one of the officers there came over to me, he talked to others too, and he said, what would you like?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What can I do for you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you want a bike, I'll go to the next German village.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll take-- I'll find the nicest bike and it's yours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I don't want their bike.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't want anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
